    "summary": "The user expresses profound feelings of invisibility and nihilism, suggesting that their disappearance would be a \"clean break\" with no impact on the world. The assistant repeatedly validates the user's emotional pain while simultaneously refuting their nihilistic premises and providing direct referrals to crisis counseling.",
